比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 分享被鬼魂袭击的经历：“我简直不敢相信” https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-shares-experience-of-being-ghosted-i-couldnt- believe-it-3764186?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=billie-eilish-shares-我简直不敢相信被鬼魂袭击的经历Damian JonesMon, 10 Jun 2024 14:15:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3764186 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她的“Hit Me Hard And Soft”世界巡演定于今年秋天开始</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-shares-experience-of-being-ghosted-i-couldnt-believe-it-3764186">Billie Eilish 分享被鬼魂困扰的经历：“我简直不敢相信”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>讲述了她被鬼魂袭击的经历。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">Billie Eilish – 《Hit Me Hard and Soft》评论：大胆、精彩、明亮</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位创作歌手最近发行了她的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">《Hit Me Hard And Soft》</a> ，她在<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/brand/p0hhgmp6" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Miss Me</em></a>播客上向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lily-allen">莉莉·艾伦</a>和米奎塔·奥利弗透露，这件事发生在去年 12 月。</p><p>她说：“我当时想，你死了吗？你真的死了吗？”并补充道，“简直令人难以置信。直到今天，[他]再也没有给我发短信。”</p><p>艾利什继续说道：“我也认识这个人很多年了，他也有一个计划，那天，我在电话里制定了一个计划，这是我的地址，下午 3 点到那里——再也没有收到他的消息。曾经。我简直不敢相信。” </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">比莉·艾利什 图片来源：Arturo Holmes/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>这位创作型歌手说，她后来发现他正在和别人约会。</p><p>她继续说道：“我当时就想‘哦’。但我不知道人们仍然这样做。我真的不知道人们会这么做。”</p><p>在同一次采访中，艾利什还表示，“当我出名时，她失去了所有的朋友”。</p><p>她说她最好的朋友佐伊仍然在她身边，但她唯一的其他朋友是她的员工。</p><p> “然后那天是我 20 岁生日，我记得环顾房间，里面只有我雇用的人。他们都比我大 15 岁或以上，”她说。</p><p>尽管如此，她说她已经与老朋友取得了联系，并结识了一些新朋友。</p><p>艾利什补充道：“整整一年前，我和一群老朋友重新取得了联系，现在我有了很多朋友。我现在有一个团队了！我真的可以为此哭泣。这是发生在我身上最伟大的事情。”</p><p>这位明星向<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-she-lost-all-of-my-friends-when-i-got-famous-3763992">艾伦透露，她曾因 2006 年首张单曲“Smile”的歌词而哭泣，但这激励她结交新朋友</a>。</p><p>她补充道：“我曾经听到这句话就想哭，因为我没有那种感觉，因为我没有朋友。我记得我想我想要那种感觉。我想听这首我在各个方面都与之相关的歌曲，听到关于朋友的那句台词，然后我会想，我的朋友们帮我度过了难关。”</p><p>与此同时，艾利什最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilishs-self-directed-video-for-chihiro-3763459">分享了她新专辑中“Chihiro”的自导视频</a>。</p><p>她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-announces-hit-me-hard-and-soft-world-tour-dates-in-uk-north-america-europe-and-australia-3751792">“Hit Me Hard And Soft”世界巡演</a>计划于今年秋天开始。英国和爱尔兰站将于 2025 年 7 月举行，其中包括在伦敦 O2 体育馆住宿六晚。在此处（英国/爱尔兰）和<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F2257710" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>（北美） <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F2257710" target="_blank" rel="noopener">查找任何剩余门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-shares-experience-of-being-ghosted-i-couldnt-believe-it-3764186">Billie Eilish 分享被鬼魂困扰的经历：“我简直不敢相信”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
